==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pitchy
<hw>Pitch"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From 1st
<er>Pitch</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Partaking of the qualities of
pitch; resembling pitch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Smeared with pitch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Black; pitch-dark; dismal.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Pitchy</xex> night.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Piteous</ent>⟦br⟧
